sub_title: XD Specialist: low-code, AI-powered decisioning and workflow automation for Autonomous Enterprises.
summary:
Specialist experience in UX Design, Design Thinking & Design Leadership. 
Solid UX Design foundation, with 22+ years of human-centred, interactive design and UX research experience.
Worked as an individual contributor, thought leader, people- and process manager.
